-cancer “epidemic”–screening and overdiagnosis. <em>N Engl J Med</em> 2014;371(19):1765–1767.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1056/NEJMp1409841">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25372084/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Korea%E2%80%99s+thyroid-cancer+%E2%80%9Cepidemic%E2%80%9D%E2%80%93screening+and+overdiagnosis&amp;author=HS+Ahn&amp;author=HJ+Kim&amp;author=HG+Welch&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=N+Engl+J+Med&amp;pages=1765-1767&amp;doi=10.1056%2FNEJMp1409841&amp;pmid=25372084">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Mandrola J, Morgan DJ. The Important but Rarely Studied Cascade of Care. <em>JAMA Netw Open</em> 2019;2(10):e1913315.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1001/jamanetworkopen.2019.13315">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31617920/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+Important+but+Rarely+Studied+Cascade+of+Care&amp;author=J+Mandrola&amp;author=DJ+Morgan&amp;publication_year=2019&amp;journal=JAMA+Netw+Open&amp;pages=e1913315&amp;doi=10.1001%2Fjamanetworkopen.2019.13315&amp;pmid=31617920">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Davenport MS. Incidental Findings and Low-Value Care. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2023;221(1):117–123.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.22.28926">Crossref</a></